{"id": "1342328381068546160", "channel_id": "1341989501467365416", "type": 0, "author_id": "1229591595544875109", "author_name": "18551801818", "author_bot": false, "content": "说的有道理，分两两篇吧", "timestamp": "2025-02-21T02:53:45.302000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1341989501467365416", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：V2.1.0.4 星辰篇调整", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1342330251287728210", "channel_id": "1341989501467365416", "type": 0, "author_id": "726748815058665574", "author_name": "shinjyo1st", "author_bot": false, "content": "其實輪換沒什麼問題 問題是星辰篇的機制不行 而且跟忘卻篇差距太大 都像是不同遊戲了\n你東西要是沒問題 玩家誰管你是星辰篇還忘卻篇", "timestamp": "2025-02-21T03:01:11.197000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 17}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1341989501467365416", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：V2.1.0.4 星辰篇调整", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1342432000694419486", "channel_id": "1341989501467365416", "type": 19, "author_id": "1342005723311243314", "author_name": "zzz279427543", "author_bot": false, "content": "抛开星辰篇内容有问题不谈，单纯分两篇最大的问题是你游本来就高的入门门槛变得更高了。入坑新手主线深浅得打忘却，融灾活动得打星辰。新人得同时学两篇同时练和抽两篇的角色。属实是太劝退了。", "timestamp": "2025-02-21T09:45:30.146000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["394079965630562304"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1342303102455386122", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1341989501467365416", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：V2.1.0.4 星辰篇调整", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1342433695910461452", "channel_id": "1341989501467365416", "type": 0, "author_id": "158132665894174721", "author_name": "ttim", "author_bot": false, "content": "這遊戲新手要練20個角色才能拿到加等級上限的素材原本已經很勸退", "timestamp": "2025-02-21T09:52:14.317000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1341989501467365416", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：V2.1.0.4 星辰篇调整", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1342434977899614228", "channel_id": "1341989501467365416", "type": 19, "author_id": "910263782293528606", "author_name": "sadanshishen", "author_bot": false, "content": "新人同时练和抽两篇角色我不太认同，基本上能在星辰篇环境下乱杀的角色在忘却篇里同样乱杀，星辰篇的高难环境现在对于新老玩家一样，把角色都砍的差不多废了，新玩家跟老玩家一样只用抽星辰篇新角就好了，比如sp朵，就算是在星辰篇如此的限制下也是在现阶段的角色里名列前茅的", "timestamp": "2025-02-21T09:57:19.967000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-02-21T10:03:08.695000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1342005723311243314"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1342432000694419486", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1341989501467365416", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：V2.1.0.4 星辰篇调整", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1342436211087904768", "channel_id": "1341989501467365416", "type": 19, "author_id": "1342005723311243314", "author_name": "zzz279427543", "author_bot": false, "content": "不完全认可，确实有星辰忘却都好用的角色，但也有新人抽的并不是这类角色，至少我群里不少重仓抽朵儿的这次星辰一来基本上都跳车了。至于后面的新卡得看怎么出了。", "timestamp": "2025-02-21T10:02:13.982000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["910263782293528606"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1342434977899614228", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1341989501467365416", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：V2.1.0.4 星辰篇调整", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
